The
best
letter
writers
express
themselves
simply.
They
avoid
long
words
where
shorter
words
will
do.
They
have
some-
thing
to
say
and
they
say
it
interestingly
and
to
the
point.
A
business
letter
should
not
be
a
literary
masterpiece,
but
that
is
not
to
say
that
it
should
not
have
style.
